WEBVTT

00:05:05.319 --> 00:05:09.375


02:05:05.319 --> 02:05:09.375
I wanted to thank all of you

02:05:09.511 --> 02:05:13.688
for enjoying this wonderful music

02:05:13.751 --> 02:05:17.299
from different parts of America,

02:05:18.298 --> 02:05:23.211
and that shows Sahaja Yoga
has a great chance –

02:05:23.924 --> 02:05:28.328
if it works out this way in America,

02:05:28.435 --> 02:05:31.625
it will work out everywhere.

02:05:32.400 --> 02:05:40.155
And it will give the peace and the joy

02:05:40.460 --> 02:05:45.302
of leading a spiritual life.

02:05:46.009 --> 02:05:50.176
I’m so very happy to see all of you here,

02:05:50.906 --> 02:05:54.160
and all of you enjoying this –

02:05:55.365 --> 02:06:00.635
very encouraging for Me

02:06:01.539 --> 02:06:06.221
and very supportive of Sahaja Yoga.

02:06:06.744 --> 02:06:09.537
I bless you all,

02:06:09.942 --> 02:06:15.072
all from America and all rest,

02:06:15.239 --> 02:06:19.223
so I’m told that you are
from different countries,

02:06:19.372 --> 02:06:23.673
so all the people I bless you.

02:06:24.774 --> 02:06:28.433
We should know we are all one,

02:06:29.036 --> 02:06:33.473
there’s no need to fight,

02:06:33.840 --> 02:06:36.697
or no need to argue,

02:06:36.864 --> 02:06:44.941
but let us enjoy the common thing
as we enjoyed this program tonight.

02:06:46.662 --> 02:06:49.884
I hope you are comfortable here

02:06:50.169 --> 02:06:52.899
– I don’t know, I haven’t seen,

02:06:53.064 --> 02:06:55.762
I had no chance to see

02:06:55.923 --> 02:06:58.415
how your things are placed,

02:06:58.603 --> 02:07:02.635
but if you have any complaints
or any problem

02:07:02.809 --> 02:07:05.087
please let me know.

02:07:34.896 --> 02:07:38.531
Thank you very much. Thank you.
